Class Receptionist

java.lang.Object
Person
Staff
Receptionist
public class Receptionist extends Staff
Subclass Receptionist which extends the abstract class Staff and implements the Schedulable interface. Represents a Receptionist in the clinic who has a lit of all the scheduled appointments.
